-- Candlestick Park Power Loss Delays Monday Night Football in San Francisco
-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 2011-12-20T01:44:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-20/candlestick-park-power-loss-delays-monday-night-football-in-san-francisco.html
The start of the Monday Night
Football game in  San Francisco  between the 49ers and the
Pittsburgh Steelers has been delayed because of a power outage
at  Candlestick Park .  The NFL said a power transformer blew out at the stadium,
causing the outage. A new start time for the game, which was set
for 8:30 p.m. ET, has not yet been announced.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  